WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.760
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.760 --> 00:00:04.560
I have a great video here for you.

00:00:04.799 --> 00:00:09.636
I have a great testimony—something that I've been believing God for, and the Lord came through.

00:00:10.187 --> 00:00:15.982
I just came on today to tell you about the goodness of God and what faith can do.

00:00:17.076 --> 00:00:24.595
First of all, I want to say thank you for all the likes, all the shares, and all the kind words in the comment section.

00:00:24.595 --> 00:00:26.017
God is so good.

00:00:26.017 --> 00:00:34.949
He told me to start this channel back at the first of the year, and to see what the Lord has done in such a short amount of time has been amazing.

00:00:35.239 --> 00:00:40.800
I just want to say thank you from the bottom of my heart, for my wife's heart, and for my children.

00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:45.306
We just want to say thank you for all the love gifts and for all of the support that you're showing us.

00:00:45.519 --> 00:00:48.000
We just want to let you know we pray for you.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:54.728
We're believing for your miracles, for a turnaround in your finances, and for healing in your bodies.

00:00:54.728 --> 00:01:03.600
I just believe that nothing is impossible to him who believes, and God is still doing miracles today.

00:01:04.062 --> 00:01:05.955
Here's a miracle that God did for me.

00:01:06.231 --> 00:01:09.493
At the beginning of this year, I had the same mower.

00:01:09.493 --> 00:01:17.733
I have a little over an acre of land that I take care of every week in the summer and the spring, and then through the fall.

00:01:17.867 --> 00:01:20.409
I have a lot of trees, and the trees drop all the leaves.

00:01:21.159 --> 00:01:24.524
I've had the same mower now for going on 20 years.

00:01:25.200 --> 00:01:32.880
The transmission belt that makes it go was slipping really bad.

00:01:33.199 --> 00:01:37.260
I started looking at how much mowers cost and pricing them.

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:43.160
For my land and how much of a mower I needed, it was going to cost thousands and thousands of dollars.

00:01:43.780 --> 00:01:49.520
I said, 'Lord, I don't want to spend that kind of money on a credit card or try to do this right now.

00:01:49.804 --> 00:01:52.778
I'm just going to use this mower as much as I can.

00:01:52.778 --> 00:01:59.480
' I anointed it with oil, started praying over my mower, and I just had to drive really slow.

00:02:01.875 --> 00:02:10.936
Here we are in August, and all through the summer, it was just driving really slow; it took me forever to mow this land.

00:02:12.765 --> 00:02:17.979
I didn't complain; it was irritating, but I just used it as prayer time.

00:02:21.100 --> 00:02:23.800
The more time I had to mow, the more time I spent praying in the spirit and seeking Him.

00:02:23.800 --> 00:02:27.610
It was just my private time mowing grass.

00:02:27.610 --> 00:02:39.134
Lo and behold, I was outside and I was weed-eating around my yard tonight when a lady from the church drove up in a truck with a mower on a trailer in the back.

00:02:42.463 --> 00:02:51.940
She jumped out of the truck and said, 'Brandon, the Lord spoke to me in my yard last night and told me to come and bless you with this mower.

00:02:56.890 --> 00:03:02.460
I bought it last year and I paid $7,000 for it.

00:03:02.460 --> 00:03:06.587
' She said it's brand new and has the bagger and everything.

00:03:16.787 --> 00:03:17.120
This mower is top of the line—the Cadillac of mowers.

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:25.020
It's one of the best mowers you can buy on the market; it doesn't get any better, really.

00:03:25.020 --> 00:03:27.227
The engine is really big.

00:03:27.227 --> 00:03:28.400
This sucker's huge.

00:03:33.090 --> 00:03:37.640
She and her husband got out and said, 'We believe the Lord spoke to us to give you this mower to use for your land.

00:03:37.640 --> 00:03:41.488
' I said, 'Are you kidding me?

00:03:41.488 --> 00:03:43.371
' and they said, 'Yeah.

00:03:43.371 --> 00:03:49.474
' She was crying and he was crying; it was a sacrificial gift.

00:03:49.474 --> 00:03:51.851
I was so taken aback by it.

00:03:51.851 --> 00:03:58.220
I just said, 'Praise God,' because I've been believing for this mower and the Lord came through.

00:04:03.599 --> 00:04:03.919
I'm not bragging about what God did; I'm rejoicing in it.

00:04:03.919 --> 00:04:08.057
I'm trying to tell you that faith can do anything.

00:04:08.057 --> 00:04:14.480
If you want to believe for anything—it doesn't matter how big or how small—God is able to provide.

00:04:21.252 --> 00:04:21.457
He came through for me again.

00:04:21.457 --> 00:04:25.307
They rolled that mower down off that trailer and said, 'Here you go.

00:04:25.307 --> 00:04:32.360
' They taught me how to use it—it took a bit because it had all these buttons and features.

00:04:32.920 --> 00:04:34.040
It was just amazing.

00:04:34.040 --> 00:04:38.464
As I said, it has the bagger for the leaves for the coming fall.

00:04:38.464 --> 00:04:41.863
Everything I ever wanted in a mower, God gave it to me today.

00:04:41.863 --> 00:04:47.173
I just want to tell you right now how good God is.

00:04:58.160 --> 00:04:58.400
God is a good God, He loves you so much, and He provided for me again today with something that was like the Cadillac of mowers.

00:04:58.400 --> 00:05:09.726
It's not like a little push mower; He gave me the best of the best of a rider and, in the world scene, I'm just telling you it doesn't get any better than that.

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:13.851
If God can do it for me, He can do it for you.

00:05:13.851 --> 00:05:21.226
I didn't complain about it; I tried to be thankful for what I had and keep a good attitude, regardless if that belt was slipping.

00:05:21.626 --> 00:05:28.060
I anointed it with oil and kept praying over it, 'Little mower, you're going to last all through the summer; you're not going to fall apart.

00:05:28.060 --> 00:05:36.759
' It kept getting worse and worse, but I kept praying in the spirit and laying hands on my mower: 'Mower, you're going to work today when I need you to work.

00:05:36.759 --> 00:05:38.400
' I told my wife, 'It's okay.

00:05:38.400 --> 00:05:40.000
It's prayer time.

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:43.554
We'll just keep a good attitude and just keep going.

00:05:43.554 --> 00:05:48.400
' I said at the end when they have a big sale sometime, we're going to find one.

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:50.639
So I looked at Craigslist and Facebook Marketplace.

00:05:50.639 --> 00:05:57.714
I was always looking, saying, 'Father, I thank You that You're going to provide something good and I'm going to get it for a good deal.

00:05:57.714 --> 00:06:01.870
' I kept thanking Him all the time, 'Thank You, Lord, that You've got this.

00:06:07.849 --> 00:06:08.080
I thank You, Father, that You supply for my needs.

00:06:08.080 --> 00:06:11.965
' I kept saying to myself, 'I'm not going to complain.

00:06:11.965 --> 00:06:23.930
' I thank You, Lord, that all my needs are met according to Your riches and glory, and this mower is even a concern to You.

00:06:23.930 --> 00:06:30.834
I kept mowing week after week, and all of a sudden, a breakthrough comes.

00:06:30.834 --> 00:06:33.291
That's the way God moves.

00:06:33.291 --> 00:06:34.251
Breakthrough comes.

00:06:34.251 --> 00:06:38.080
Faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:06:38.080 --> 00:06:50.319
The same faith that will move a mountain will produce a mower, a healing, or whatever you need—an electric bill paid or some food for your children.

00:06:50.319 --> 00:06:51.691
God is a provider.

00:06:51.691 --> 00:06:54.080
I'm encouraged because it was a great breakthrough.

00:06:54.080 --> 00:07:02.280
When that mower turned that corner tonight when I was out there weed-eating in my yard, I thought, 'What in the world?

00:07:02.280 --> 00:07:10.639
' I noticed the truck and thought they were coming to help me mow; I had no idea that they were going to bless me with this high-dollar mower.

00:07:13.240 --> 00:07:15.319
I just wanted to give God the praise for it.

00:07:15.319 --> 00:07:19.320
The Lord has been speaking to me about 2024.

00:07:19.920 --> 00:07:28.720
I want you all to be encouraged; there is a major financial shifting about to take place.

00:07:29.264 --> 00:07:34.450
You need to get the Word down inside of you.

00:07:37.218 --> 00:07:48.840
I was driving down the road praying in the spirit and the Lord warned me, 'Brandon, there are very sobering days coming to America and around the world.

00:07:48.840 --> 00:07:50.560
' Very sobering days.

00:07:50.560 --> 00:07:53.169
And I thought, "Well, that doesn't sound like a real good word.

00:07:53.169 --> 00:07:58.319
" He said, "But Brandon, what is the opposite of being sober?

00:07:58.319 --> 00:08:00.422
" He said, "Being drunk.

00:08:01.474 --> 00:08:04.920
You need to be filled with the Holy Ghost.

00:08:04.920 --> 00:08:10.520
You need to stay full with the Holy Ghost at all times to get through the days ahead.

00:08:10.520 --> 00:08:22.462
You need to get laughter down on the inside of you and get that Holy Ghost bubbling up on the inside of you to make it for what's coming.

00:08:23.564 --> 00:08:25.956
" He told me, he said, "Do you remember, son?

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:28.720
" And this is just the way we talk.

00:08:28.720 --> 00:08:32.259
"Do you remember about Mary Poppins whenever they were drinking the stuff?

00:08:36.560 --> 00:08:37.740
I love to laugh.

00:08:37.740 --> 00:08:39.936
" He said, "That's the way you need to be.

00:08:39.936 --> 00:08:40.703
I love to laugh.

00:08:40.703 --> 00:08:44.239
You need to be filled with the Holy Ghost and laughter.

00:08:44.239 --> 00:08:57.632
" And I've told you all this before, but the Lord reminded me again to tell you: you need to be filled with a refreshing, drinking of the spirit through praise.

00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:08.102
You need to get into the spirit of praise in your house, worshiping Him and thanksgiving and praise and adoration.

00:09:08.102 --> 00:09:18.469
"God, thank you for all that you've done for my home," and get in that vein because when praises go up, blessings come down.

00:09:21.086 --> 00:09:24.044
I'm telling you, I was in a state of prayer last night.

00:09:24.044 --> 00:09:34.549
I was trying to tell you, and I kind of skipped around here about 2024 and what He was warning me about, and it's going to be a year that we soar.

00:09:46.338 --> 00:09:47.760
It's time for the body of Christ to start taking the dominion and our authority over the land and walking in a presence on our lives.

00:09:51.360 --> 00:09:51.608
We will soar in '24.

00:09:51.608 --> 00:09:53.591
Remember that it's a good year.

00:09:57.059 --> 00:09:57.280
It's not going to be a bad year.

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:05.279
And what the devil meant for bad, God will turn it for good in your favor if you just grab hold of it.

00:10:05.279 --> 00:10:09.310
I'm telling you, it's not a time to start to shrink back.

00:10:18.250 --> 00:10:18.600
It's time to take the land.

00:10:18.600 --> 00:10:23.720
It's time to take what God has given us and go with boldness.

00:10:23.720 --> 00:10:31.530
Like Joshua, we're going to go and walk around the walls of Jericho and we're going to give a great shout.

00:10:32.673 --> 00:10:37.173
And those walls that the devil has tried to put up over the years are coming down.

00:10:39.509 --> 00:10:39.739
It's time for the walls to come down.

00:10:39.739 --> 00:10:42.676
But how they did it was a shout of praise.

00:10:42.676 --> 00:10:44.453
Oh, glory, glory, glory.

00:10:44.453 --> 00:10:46.739
Glory to God in the highest.

00:10:51.252 --> 00:11:00.560
And they blew their trumpets and bam, all the walls came down through a great earthquake and it shook those walls and they went in and they took the city of Jericho.

00:11:00.560 --> 00:11:06.480
Now, it's time for us to do the same things like they did of old.

00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:10.320
It's time for us to walk in revival.

00:11:10.320 --> 00:11:15.840
It's time for us to be able to take dominion and authority over our children.

00:11:32.600 --> 00:11:33.040
And we need to know who we are in Christ.

00:11:33.040 --> 00:11:38.060
Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:11:49.060 --> 00:11:49.350
And the same Jesus that was raised from the dead is dwelling on the inside of you in the Holy Spirit.

00:11:49.350 --> 00:11:50.220
He's inside of you.

00:11:50.220 --> 00:11:52.560
And it's time to walk in abundance.

00:11:52.560 --> 00:11:55.371
It's time to walk in favor.

00:11:55.371 --> 00:12:01.920
It's time to turn the circumstances around in your life.

00:12:02.880 --> 00:12:04.630
God is no respecter of persons.

00:12:04.630 --> 00:12:12.011
I'm telling you all, I saw the blessing and the favor of God even yesterday.

00:12:12.011 --> 00:12:14.469
You've got to change it.

00:12:18.959 --> 00:12:19.782
What you said today is what you'll be living tomorrow.

00:12:25.466 --> 00:12:26.373
If you don't like where you're living right now, check what you said yesterday.

00:12:26.373 --> 00:12:28.879
I'm trying to tell you something.

00:12:28.879 --> 00:12:30.179
It's very important.

00:12:30.179 --> 00:12:35.920
Your words, speaking out of your mouth, decreeing a thing is what you are living.

00:12:35.920 --> 00:12:37.680
That's the fruit.

00:12:37.680 --> 00:12:45.728
Every seed you sow through your words or through financial giving will produce: some 30, some 60, and 100fold.

00:12:45.728 --> 00:12:52.320
If you need a miracle in your finances, you need to sow into good ground.

00:12:52.960 --> 00:12:56.560
You need to believe God because the harvest comes by sowing seed.

00:12:56.560 --> 00:13:00.739
If you're not sowing seed, you can't believe God for a harvest.

00:13:00.739 --> 00:13:01.439
I tithe.

00:13:01.439 --> 00:13:04.230
I give regularly as much as I can.

00:13:08.480 --> 00:13:08.720
And I sow those seeds and I believe and He provides.

00:13:18.360 --> 00:13:18.589
But if you're not sowing seed, don't expect a harvest in that area.

00:13:18.589 --> 00:13:20.377
What you sow, you'll reap.

00:13:20.377 --> 00:13:23.860
Whatsoever a man soweth, that shall he also reap.

00:13:23.860 --> 00:13:25.179
It's a law.

00:13:25.179 --> 00:13:30.070
If you sow corn into the ground, you're going to reap back corn.

00:13:30.070 --> 00:13:33.840
If you sow peas into the ground, you're going to reap back peas.

00:13:33.840 --> 00:13:36.902
If you sow potatoes and so on, the same thing.

00:13:41.700 --> 00:13:41.970
You sow into the kingdom of God and you bless ministries.

00:13:41.970 --> 00:13:51.740
You help people out and God's going to bless you: good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over, shall men give unto your bosom.

00:13:51.740 --> 00:13:54.867
He'll give you creative ideas to get wealth.

00:13:54.867 --> 00:14:01.040
He'll bless you so that you can be a blessing to others.

00:14:01.040 --> 00:14:04.114
It's not always about hoarding things on yourself.

00:14:04.114 --> 00:14:10.339
It's about being a blessing to the person in the line at the grocery store.

00:14:10.339 --> 00:14:16.206
They may not have grocery money to buy any groceries.

00:14:16.206 --> 00:14:28.827
They may be running low, but you go in there and you show the love of God, and the Holy Ghost speaks to you and he tells you, "Hey, you see that person right there?

00:14:33.173 --> 00:14:33.747
They don't have the money to buy their groceries.

00:14:33.747 --> 00:14:40.844
They're running real low on finances, but you can tell them Jesus loves them and buy their groceries today.

00:14:52.910 --> 00:14:53.240
" But you can't do that broke.

00:14:56.840 --> 00:14:57.360
You can't do that bound.

00:14:57.360 --> 00:15:02.720
You've got to be treading water, not sinking in the water.

00:15:02.720 --> 00:15:06.651
We've got to be above and not beneath.

00:15:06.651 --> 00:15:11.822
We've got to go through and not go under.

00:15:11.822 --> 00:15:16.764
God has the cattle on a thousand hills and He has given it to us.

00:15:16.764 --> 00:15:20.709
He said, "I've given you dominion and authority and power in this earth.

00:15:20.709 --> 00:15:22.700
Go and take dominion.

00:15:22.700 --> 00:15:26.347
Subdue it just like He told Adam.

00:15:32.360 --> 00:15:36.142
" And we have that same power on the inside of us to subdue and take dominion and authority over things.

00:15:36.142 --> 00:15:41.280
And God wants us to be a blessing to our neighbor.

00:15:41.280 --> 00:15:46.949
What's coming is going to be bad in the natural.

00:15:46.949 --> 00:15:49.714
I hope you all understand me.

00:15:49.714 --> 00:15:54.999
I do not try to preach fear, but I need to warn you again.

00:15:54.999 --> 00:15:56.369
Listen to me.

00:16:04.040 --> 00:16:04.349
A great shaking is coming.

00:16:04.349 --> 00:16:07.644
It is a massive shaking.

00:16:07.644 --> 00:16:11.440
It will be very hard for some people.

00:16:16.444 --> 00:16:21.146
And if you are not able to be a blessing to your neighbors around you that don't know Jesus Christ, you're missing it.

00:16:21.146 --> 00:16:23.976
We've got to come up another level.

00:16:23.976 --> 00:16:27.383
I saw it again in the spirit.

00:16:27.383 --> 00:16:30.479
I saw a great financial harvest.

00:16:30.479 --> 00:16:32.772
They were like dominoes stacked up.

00:16:33.519 --> 00:16:36.089
And I saw the years and the months ahead.

00:16:36.906 --> 00:16:43.440
And the Lord painted it out in front of me and He told me, He said, "There's going to be a financial shifting.

00:16:43.440 --> 00:16:45.885
There's going to be a catastrophic event.

00:16:45.885 --> 00:16:48.834
There's going to be an outpouring of my spirit.

00:16:48.834 --> 00:16:52.639
There's going to be a great harvest of souls.

00:16:52.639 --> 00:16:56.680
" But He told me, He said, "Brandon, that's what I'm trying to tell you again.

00:16:56.680 --> 00:16:58.533
2024 you will soar.

00:16:58.533 --> 00:17:01.325
It's time to come up another level.

00:17:01.325 --> 00:17:04.351
It's time to do things greater.

00:17:14.710 --> 00:17:14.980
I will provide all your needs according to My riches in glory.

00:17:23.661 --> 00:17:24.079
" And I saw into 2024, and 2024 is not a bad year.

00:17:24.079 --> 00:17:25.220
It's a blessed year.

00:17:25.220 --> 00:17:25.410
I'm telling you.

00:17:25.410 --> 00:17:28.693
But like I said, it's like a coin.

00:17:28.693 --> 00:17:33.679
You can either focus on the bad or you can focus on the good.

00:17:33.679 --> 00:17:34.720
It's that thin.

00:17:34.720 --> 00:17:36.194
But it's a choice.

00:17:36.194 --> 00:17:44.479
You can praise Him through the storm and speak to your storm and tell it to be still, or you can let the storm overtake you.

00:17:44.479 --> 00:17:48.293
But you are in charge of your destiny.

00:17:48.293 --> 00:17:52.760
But you speaking out of your mouth, "Well, my life's never going to change.

00:17:52.760 --> 00:17:54.868
My life's never going to get better.

00:17:54.868 --> 00:18:03.680
All things are falling apart for me," you're going to start living it.

00:18:06.780 --> 00:18:08.580
You can look around you and think, "Man, my life is looking terrible.

00:18:08.580 --> 00:18:11.120
My car is falling apart.

00:18:11.120 --> 00:18:13.280
My house has a leaky roof.

00:18:13.280 --> 00:18:26.034
" But I'm telling you, a lot of what we live today is what we spoke 10 years ago, what we believed 5 years ago.

00:18:33.360 --> 00:18:33.650
Life and death are in the power of your tongue.

00:18:42.640 --> 00:18:42.937
And the Bible also says your tongue is the pen of a ready writer.

00:18:47.867 --> 00:18:48.253
And so you are writing your destiny, your future, out by what you speak.

00:18:48.253 --> 00:18:56.760
If you're saying things out of your mouth that are ugly and bad and you're cursing your wife—"Well, you're a no-good so-and-so"—guess what?

00:18:56.760 --> 00:19:02.000
You're going to start to reap a no-good so-and-so because you have authority over your house, husbands.

00:19:06.960 --> 00:19:07.340
You have authority over your children.

00:19:12.293 --> 00:19:12.676
You have authority over your wife.

00:19:12.676 --> 00:19:15.399
God gave you dominion over that home.

00:19:15.399 --> 00:19:22.640
And when you start speaking trash over your kids—"Well, Johnny, he's out there and he's just a no-good so-and-so.

00:19:22.640 --> 00:19:27.371
He's out doing drugs, sleeping around, doing all this stuff"—no, you've got to change your words.

00:19:27.371 --> 00:19:37.600
You've got to start speaking into that circumstance, saying, "No, Johnny's full of the Holy Ghost.

00:19:37.600 --> 00:19:44.736
He's full of the life and the power of God, and God's going to deliver him and use him for the kingdom.

00:19:55.166 --> 00:19:55.520
Things are going to get better in Johnny's life.

00:19:59.253 --> 00:20:04.533
" I don't know what's going to happen to the person next door, but as for me and my house, we will serve the Lord.

00:20:05.771 --> 00:20:08.389
And that's the kind of words you've got to start saying.

00:20:08.389 --> 00:20:11.120
You've got to speak life into your circumstances.

00:20:11.120 --> 00:20:15.410
You've got to speak life into your children.

00:20:15.410 --> 00:20:18.339
You've got to speak life into your wife.

00:20:18.339 --> 00:20:21.973
And wives, you need to speak life into your husband.

00:20:24.880 --> 00:20:26.169
You don't need to be out cursing him: "Oh, he's just a drunk.

00:20:26.169 --> 00:20:28.100
" No, he's not a drunk.

00:20:28.100 --> 00:20:30.176
He's full of the Holy Ghost.

00:20:30.176 --> 00:20:32.720
He's full of the wine of the Holy Ghost.

00:20:32.720 --> 00:20:36.594
He's going to be leading our family into victory.

00:20:36.594 --> 00:20:43.360
He's not going to be out doing bars and cheating and doing all that stuff.

00:20:43.360 --> 00:20:51.840
He's going to be in here preaching the word of God and leading this family into victory.

00:21:04.910 --> 00:21:05.340
You have to speak to your circumstances.

00:21:05.340 --> 00:21:07.059
Do you understand?

00:21:12.846 --> 00:21:15.139
Like I told you a thousand times, it feels like your mountain has to hear your voice.

00:21:15.139 --> 00:21:27.640
But what you live—I'll say it again—what you're living right now, what you're having in your life right now is a result of what you said yesterday.

00:21:27.640 --> 00:21:31.919
Remember that you have got to speak life into your circumstances.

00:21:31.919 --> 00:21:37.929
You have to because life and death is in the power of the tongue.

00:21:47.240 --> 00:21:48.600
It's so important that you hear what I'm telling you because a lot of you—I see what you're saying: "Well, God works in your life but he doesn't work in mine.

00:21:54.377 --> 00:21:54.754
" You know why?

00:21:54.754 --> 00:21:57.102
Because that's what you believe.

00:21:57.102 --> 00:22:00.459
Out of the abundance of the heart, the mouth speaks.

00:22:08.880 --> 00:22:09.120
The Bible says that what you believe in your heart, you're going to say out of your mouth.

00:22:12.420 --> 00:22:17.588
You can always pinpoint somebody and where they are in their faith because of what they're saying out of their mouth.

00:22:20.693 --> 00:22:25.726
I can just get around you for five minutes to have a conversation and ask you certain questions about your life.

00:22:30.173 --> 00:22:30.559
What do you say about your life?

00:22:30.559 --> 00:22:33.290
What are you saying about your circumstances?

00:22:33.290 --> 00:22:35.669
Because I can pinpoint your faith real quick.

00:22:39.219 --> 00:22:39.449
You will never hear me speak bad about my kids, ever.

00:22:40.536 --> 00:22:45.820
I tell you examples of things to help you, but I'm telling you, I never even would let anybody speak the word "autism" out of their mouth.

00:22:45.820 --> 00:22:50.080
If you spoke "autism" over my daughter, I would want to punch you in the face.

00:22:50.080 --> 00:22:51.679
That's how much it upset me.

00:22:51.679 --> 00:22:54.587
I'd be like, "No, you ain't speaking that trash over my child.

00:22:54.587 --> 00:22:56.800
She's healed by the stripes of Jesus.

00:23:01.479 --> 00:23:04.240
" It's an illustration I'm trying to tell you.

00:23:04.240 --> 00:23:09.450
Sometimes I tell you, "This is what we're overcoming," but we don't speak that word in our house.

00:23:09.450 --> 00:23:10.950
It's like speaking death.

00:23:10.950 --> 00:23:12.297
That's a death word.

00:23:12.297 --> 00:23:14.000
We're not speaking that; we speak life.

00:23:14.000 --> 00:23:16.626
Megan is healed by the stripes of Jesus.

00:23:16.626 --> 00:23:18.480
Megan has the mind of Christ.

00:23:18.480 --> 00:23:24.686
Megan can do all things through Christ who's in her.

00:23:29.719 --> 00:23:30.139
I'm not moved by what I see.

00:23:30.139 --> 00:23:33.360
I'm not moved by what I feel right now.

00:23:33.360 --> 00:23:44.789
Yeah, she may have had a temper tantrum and she may be flipping out and doing her thing and stemming and doing all this stuff, but God, I thank you, Lord, that those things are subject to change.

00:23:46.710 --> 00:23:52.520
I am not moved by what she's doing right now when she's having an anger fit or doing something.

00:23:59.564 --> 00:23:59.849
I just pray over her mind: "Father, I lay hands on her.

00:23:59.849 --> 00:24:04.360
I bind any kind of demonic disturbances off of you, baby.

00:24:07.760 --> 00:24:08.800
You are healed in the name of Jesus.

00:24:08.800 --> 00:24:13.259
I speak to your brain cells to line up with the word of God.

00:24:13.259 --> 00:24:18.729
I speak to any damage in your body that's been caused by vaccinations to be healed in Jesus' name.

00:24:19.342 --> 00:24:27.573
" You are a creative, miracle-working God, and I believe with all my heart that You raised Christ from the dead and You healed me by His stripes.

00:24:27.796 --> 00:24:28.960
I stand on that.

00:24:28.960 --> 00:24:31.840
I'm not moved by what I see.

00:24:31.840 --> 00:24:38.488
I'm not moved by what I feel; I'm moved by what the word says.

00:24:38.488 --> 00:24:39.799
God is a good God.

00:24:39.799 --> 00:24:43.086
Remember this, regardless of what your circumstances are saying around you: No.

00:24:43.086 --> 00:25:01.630
Regardless of how bad it may look—you may have the worst conditions and it doesn't look like it's changed—but if you keep on keeping on, if you keep speaking and you keep declaring and you keep looking at your circumstances, it's going to change.

00:25:01.630 --> 00:25:07.020
It takes time sometimes to move a big ship and to turn a huge ocean liner.

00:25:18.720 --> 00:25:18.960
It takes a little bit to turn that ship.

00:25:18.960 --> 00:25:25.900
Sometimes it takes a little bit because you've been speaking so much trash out of your mouth for so long.

00:25:25.900 --> 00:25:28.650
It may take a little bit, but don't give up.

00:25:28.650 --> 00:25:30.440
Don't give in to it.

00:25:32.453 --> 00:25:40.000
The devil might come by and whisper in your ear, telling you your life's never going to change, you're going to be this way forever, and there's no God that hears your prayers.

00:25:40.000 --> 00:25:47.320
But I'm telling you this, God is faithful and He's going to set you free with the same power that He set me free with.

00:25:47.320 --> 00:25:49.600
He loves you.

00:25:49.600 --> 00:25:50.649
Don't get weary in well-doing.

00:25:50.649 --> 00:25:52.540
Keep your faith stirred up.

00:25:52.540 --> 00:25:55.279
You've got to get in the word every day.

00:25:55.279 --> 00:26:02.559
You've got to get in prayer every day because you have to keep filling your spirit up with that word.

00:26:02.559 --> 00:26:04.571
Find the scripture.

00:26:04.571 --> 00:26:11.840
I've said it before and I'll say it again: you've got to find scriptures pertaining to what you're believing for.

00:26:11.840 --> 00:26:17.100
You've got to get that word down inside of your heart because in those words, that's what brings freedom.

00:26:23.820 --> 00:26:24.040
You shall know the truth, and the truth will set you free.

00:26:25.893 --> 00:26:28.590
But I'm telling you, if you keep speaking trash out of your mouth, you're going to live it.

00:26:28.590 --> 00:26:32.984
I've lived it; I saw it happen when I was growing up.

00:26:32.984 --> 00:26:39.712
A lot of times my mom would speak things out of her mouth that she didn't believe in her heart because whatever was at the abundance of the heart, the mouth speaks, what I tell you.

00:26:41.600 --> 00:26:41.839
And we kept going around the mountain.

00:26:41.839 --> 00:26:46.279
But I'm telling you, my mother started speaking better out of her mouth.

00:26:46.279 --> 00:26:47.851
She lives it now.

00:26:47.851 --> 00:26:51.120
She started speaking positive out of her mouth.

00:26:51.120 --> 00:26:55.100
She started saying things over us: "It's going to get better.

00:26:55.884 --> 00:27:00.822
" And I'm telling you, after the third kid, my little brother, he had it a lot better than what I had it.

00:27:00.822 --> 00:27:04.284
When I first started out, we had it real rough.

00:27:04.284 --> 00:27:10.520
But when she started getting the word of faith and all that word down inside of her, it started changing.

00:27:10.520 --> 00:27:13.360
My little brother has a totally different life than what I had.

00:27:13.360 --> 00:27:17.679
But I'm telling you this, you can change your circumstances by your words.

00:27:20.297 --> 00:27:20.708
You need to understand how powerful your words are.

00:27:29.120 --> 00:27:29.400
And I hope I haven't become boring, but I'm just trying to tell you what's changed my life.

00:27:29.400 --> 00:27:32.142
That's what I kept saying about the mower.

00:27:32.142 --> 00:27:33.840
God is a good God.

00:27:33.840 --> 00:27:37.619
He's going to take care of me.

00:27:37.619 --> 00:27:49.152
Even whenever it didn't look like it was going to and the summer is almost over, but right when it's almost time to start doing the leaves, God says, "Brennan, I got your back.

00:27:49.727 --> 00:27:51.600
I got you.

00:27:51.600 --> 00:28:01.234
" Maybe He was talking to that sister in the church for weeks ahead and she was resisting it.

00:28:04.906 --> 00:28:09.760
A lot of times, this is what I want to tell you: when God speaks to you to be obedient and to do something, do it immediately.

00:28:09.760 --> 00:28:15.440
Because if you don't, He'll bring that person who you're believing for and you're sowing those seeds.

00:28:16.729 --> 00:28:17.760
It may take you a long time.

00:28:17.760 --> 00:28:20.480
This might be something that I'm reaping.

00:28:22.399 --> 00:28:24.000
He might be telling you, 'You need to do this, this, and this.

00:28:24.000 --> 00:28:28.930
' He'll bring that same kind of person around you who was in rebellion.

00:28:28.930 --> 00:28:41.540
Basically, if he told them a long time ago, 'I wanted to give that mower to them back in June or May when the season first started,' and they resisted it—'Oh, I don't feel like it.

00:28:44.139 --> 00:28:44.399
I don't want to do that.

00:28:46.400 --> 00:28:51.180
I just paid $7,000 for that'—and they wrestle with it, the Lord keeps putting it on their heart: 'I want you to do this for Brandon.

00:28:51.180 --> 00:28:54.820
' 'I don't feel like doing that right now, Lord.

00:28:54.820 --> 00:28:56.920
' Don't sow those kind of seeds.

00:28:56.920 --> 00:29:03.199
When God speaks to you to do something, be quick to obey because that's the kind of seed you'll reap back.

00:29:03.199 --> 00:29:07.879
When God speaks to somebody's heart to help you out, be quick to obey.

00:29:07.879 --> 00:29:10.470
He'll start speaking to someone's heart to sow fast to you.

00:29:13.543 --> 00:29:15.180
You could be waiting on your miracle sometimes and ask, 'Where is it, Lord?

00:29:15.180 --> 00:29:17.306
' like in my situation.

00:29:21.490 --> 00:29:22.940
But there've been times he's told me, 'I want you to give a watch away.

00:29:22.940 --> 00:29:27.451
' I don't want to give that watch away because I love watches.

00:29:27.451 --> 00:29:29.653
Watches are a big deal to me.

00:29:29.653 --> 00:29:33.316
I've given seven watches away, and the Lord tells me it's like a ministry to me.

00:29:33.316 --> 00:29:34.103
I love watches.

00:29:38.171 --> 00:29:42.440
So I give these watches away, and the Lord said, 'See that person over there in church?

00:29:42.440 --> 00:29:46.267
I want you to.

00:29:46.267 --> 00:29:56.880
' My first watch I ever gave away, I was 15 years old and I paid $400 for it; it was a Seiko.

00:29:56.880 --> 00:30:03.919
It was really dear to me because it was one of those kinetic ones that you could move your arm and it would charge itself.

00:30:09.680 --> 00:30:09.960
And the Lord spoke to me, 'I want you to give that watch to the youth pastor.

00:30:09.960 --> 00:30:15.303
' It was really nice back then; for me, that was a lot of money.

00:30:25.172 --> 00:30:25.377
It took me forever to save up for that watch.

00:30:40.011 --> 00:30:40.183
I kept resisting it and was like, 'Please Lord, I don't want to give that watch away.

00:30:40.183 --> 00:30:50.160
' It took me months to save for that watch because I was sacking groceries, just putting groceries up, and I only made minimum wage.

00:30:50.160 --> 00:30:51.840
Back then, that was nothing.

00:30:51.840 --> 00:31:00.333
I kept resisting it and I didn't want to sow, but I had to do my tithes and offerings and everything.

00:31:00.587 --> 00:31:03.720
The Lord said, 'I want you to give that watch to him.

00:31:03.720 --> 00:31:10.640
' One day I was at church and he walked by me, and the Lord said, 'Give that watch to him right now.

00:31:12.579 --> 00:31:14.240
I want you to be obedient to what I told you to do.

00:31:14.240 --> 00:31:17.769
' So I took my watch off and I said, 'Hey, pastor.

00:31:30.568 --> 00:31:30.790
The Lord spoke to me to give this watch to you.

00:31:30.790 --> 00:31:36.860
This is a sacrificial gift, and it's painful for my flesh because it took me over three months to save up for this.

00:31:36.860 --> 00:31:37.430
400 bucks.

00:31:37.430 --> 00:31:40.459
' So I gave it to him and I prayed over him.

00:31:41.375 --> 00:31:42.336
I cried as I did it.

00:31:42.336 --> 00:31:46.674
But I'm trying to tell you, God is faithful and he always provides another watch.

00:31:46.674 --> 00:31:50.199
He always takes care of things.

00:31:50.199 --> 00:31:55.919
I started sowing those watches, and the Lord gives me better watches.

00:31:55.919 --> 00:31:59.467
So this is a thing for me.

00:32:12.053 --> 00:32:12.800
I'm wanting you to understand that sometimes God will speak to your heart and tell you to do something that's not always comfortable to your flesh.

00:32:12.800 --> 00:32:21.537
It wasn't comfortable to the lady that gave me the $7,000 mower she just bought over a year ago.

00:32:21.537 --> 00:32:23.260
It was almost brand new.

00:32:23.260 --> 00:32:24.159
It's not comfortable sometimes.

00:32:24.159 --> 00:32:27.664
It makes you want to go 'ooh,' but there's reward in it.

00:32:27.664 --> 00:32:31.648
There've been so many times that I sow and it's painful.

00:32:31.648 --> 00:32:35.139
But you have to move in faith for your circumstances.

00:32:35.139 --> 00:32:44.532
You've got to put your faith into motion and do things that are uncomfortable.

00:32:44.532 --> 00:32:48.407
God is a faithful God.

00:32:51.740 --> 00:32:57.970
And if you sow into good ground and you sow and you do these things, God will always come through for you.

00:32:57.970 --> 00:33:01.892
I'm just trying to tell you what I've lived, y'all.

00:33:01.892 --> 00:33:03.742
I do it all the time.

00:33:04.338 --> 00:33:05.626
And God is a faithful God.

00:33:05.626 --> 00:33:16.971
So if the Lord tells you to bless your church or the lady at the grocery store and you don't want to help, she might be down to her last $50.

00:33:20.240 --> 00:33:30.330
You could be the greatest influence and the greatest blessing to that person at that moment and just tell them, 'Jesus loves you and I just want to pray for you.

00:33:30.330 --> 00:33:32.279
' They may go, 'I need prayer.

00:33:32.279 --> 00:33:38.673
' Kind of like when I prayed for the man that had the bad lung problem.

00:33:38.673 --> 00:33:45.088
He was desperate and needed his miracle right then, or he was getting ready to die.

00:33:45.088 --> 00:33:49.153
What an opportunity to be a blessing!

00:33:49.153 --> 00:33:53.139
I see the comment section, and I'm just trying to go by what I see.

00:33:53.139 --> 00:33:57.177
A lady's talking about how she's broke and can't pay for her food.

00:33:59.937 --> 00:34:00.168
I'm telling you how God's always provided for me.

00:34:05.342 --> 00:34:06.925
I wanted to tell you a testimony about what God did for me this evening just yesterday.

00:34:07.256 --> 00:34:13.332
God's so faithful and God will take care of you if you believe him.

00:34:13.332 --> 00:34:18.027
But you have to start speaking and believing better.

00:34:18.027 --> 00:34:26.353
When you do, God's going to turn your mountain around.

00:34:26.353 --> 00:34:29.440
He's a mountain-dissolving God.

00:34:34.423 --> 00:34:37.880
We are in the greatest days for the body of Christ to be a light and to be the salt.

00:34:37.880 --> 00:34:38.800
It's a choice.

00:34:38.800 --> 00:34:41.540
But Jesus needs us to be obedient.

00:34:41.540 --> 00:34:46.746
If we're not, we're not doing what he's called us to do.

00:34:46.746 --> 00:34:53.406
He's ready to come back, but he's wanting those souls coming in.

00:34:53.406 --> 00:35:06.906
If you have something on your heart and you need direction, or for preaching like these little sermons I'm doing, tell me, 'Hey, I'm believing for this.

00:35:06.906 --> 00:35:17.568
' I'm trying to give you encouragement by telling you how my wife and I have lived this.

00:35:17.568 --> 00:35:19.587
We're not perfect.

00:35:19.587 --> 00:35:25.920
One time we had our maternity and the doctor's bills were thousands of dollars.

00:35:32.770 --> 00:35:32.960
We were broke.

00:35:33.783 --> 00:35:37.359
I was working at the church and we were real desperate.

00:35:39.300 --> 00:35:43.200
The hospital sent the bill to a collection agency, and they were going to garnish our wages.

00:35:43.200 --> 00:35:47.100
It's the way it is here in Oklahoma.

00:35:47.100 --> 00:35:51.790
If you don't pay your bills, they're able to come after you.

00:35:51.790 --> 00:35:57.234
Rightfully so, I owed the money, but I just didn't have it.

00:35:57.234 --> 00:35:59.830
We were living on food stamps.

00:36:10.628 --> 00:36:10.810
They were saying, 'We're going to garnish your checks.

00:36:10.810 --> 00:36:14.187
' We were like, 'God, what are we going to do?

00:36:14.187 --> 00:36:16.390
' We couldn't even pay our rent.

00:36:16.390 --> 00:36:18.640
So we were just standing by faith.

00:36:22.632 --> 00:36:22.848
And this is another circumstance.

00:36:22.848 --> 00:36:30.026
This was something that was really dear to me at the time because God came through.

00:36:36.200 --> 00:36:36.549
I was cleaning the bathrooms of the church.

00:36:37.599 --> 00:36:46.480
I was keeping my head up and I said, "God, they're coming after my check, they're going to take part of it, and I don't have it.

00:36:46.480 --> 00:36:48.891
We're going to go without food again.

00:36:58.200 --> 00:36:58.640
" I was just whining inside my heart, trying to keep my faith up.

00:36:58.640 --> 00:37:01.070
Some people in the church...

00:37:13.851 --> 00:37:14.286
we didn't tell anybody anything because I'm not a person who manipulates.

00:37:14.286 --> 00:37:18.079
Don't be a person who is manipulating people by the ministry of hints.

00:37:18.079 --> 00:37:19.719
Don't do that.

00:37:19.719 --> 00:37:22.091
God is your provider.

00:37:22.091 --> 00:37:23.554
Man is not.

00:37:23.554 --> 00:37:27.470
You need to understand that.

00:37:27.470 --> 00:37:50.239
Don't go around telling people at church, "Well, I'm having a hard time and I can't pay my bills.

00:37:50.239 --> 00:37:51.440
" Tell God and rejoice.

00:37:51.440 --> 00:37:53.736
Keep your eyes on Jesus.

00:37:53.736 --> 00:37:56.663
Don't put your eyes on man.

00:37:56.663 --> 00:38:01.033
My wife, Diana, was working.

00:38:01.033 --> 00:38:03.973
We were doing the best we could.

00:38:05.390 --> 00:38:10.594
I was in there cleaning and I got a call on my radio: "Hey, come to the front.

00:38:14.640 --> 00:38:22.800
" I went up to the front and there was a lady there.

00:38:22.800 --> 00:38:42.293
She said, "The Lord told me to write you a check to pay off your hospital bills.

00:38:42.293 --> 00:38:48.835
" It took my breath away because I was so desperate.

00:38:48.835 --> 00:38:56.373
I called my wife and said, "Hey, babe, look what Jesus just did.

00:38:56.373 --> 00:38:59.977
" She gave me a check for $3,500.

00:38:59.977 --> 00:39:08.306
She said, "The Lord told me to give you this to pay off your hospital bills, what you still owed.

00:39:08.760 --> 00:39:10.811
" And God took care of all of it.

00:39:22.178 --> 00:39:22.409
We were right there at the point of them garnishing my wages.

00:39:22.409 --> 00:39:26.960
But I'm trying to tell you, God is a faithful God.

00:39:30.869 --> 00:39:32.731
And if you believe him, nothing is impossible to him who believes.

00:39:56.640 --> 00:39:56.880
So let me pray for you right now.

00:39:56.880 --> 00:39:58.560
Will you bow your heads?

00:39:58.560 --> 00:40:01.636
I'm going to believe God.

00:40:05.620 --> 00:40:05.970
You may need a financial miracle or breakthrough.

00:40:07.760 --> 00:40:09.200
You may need healing in your body.

00:40:09.200 --> 00:40:11.680
I don't know what circumstances you are in, but I know it doesn't matter what it is.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
All things are possible.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Nothing is too big.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
So, Father, right now, just stretch your hands out to me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
I'm going to believe God with you right now.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Wherever you are, you might be all around the world.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
You may be down to your last cup of rice.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
There are some people all over the place that I'm ministering to right now.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
You may be to your last cup of beans.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Who knows?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
But I know this: God's a multiplier.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
God's a God that provides.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
So, Father, right now in the name of Jesus, I speak to their circumstances.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
I agree with my brothers and sisters right now.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
We speak life out of our mouths concerning our circumstances.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
We turn our circumstances around by faith.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
You said that nothing is impossible to him who believes.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
And so, Father, right now in the name of Jesus, we call forth the harvest.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
We send our angels out from the north, the south, the east, and the west to bring the money they need.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Father, I thank you, Lord.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
Go, ministering spirits, go and cause the money and the food to come forth.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Father, I speak to the needs.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
I speak to the mountain: you go, in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.400
We call forth blessing and increase and multiplied favor according to Malachi and Deuteronomy 28, that everything we put our hands to will prosper.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
